{
  "texts": [
    "They first analyzed the answers posted in CQA and the projects submitted in OSS to score developer expertise in the two communities, respectively.",
    "They then computed the final expertise by summing up the two scores.",
    "However, they did not consider the interactions among developers, which have implications for evaluating the expertise of developers.",
    "Furthermore, most approaches to developer expertise profiling ignore the fact that developer expertise evolves over time due to learning or forgetting.",
    "To fill this gap, Yan et al. [701] and Song et al."
  ]
}